VisionCraft

This project combines original VisionCraft code with vendored third-party components.

## Vendored components

| Component | Location | License |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| ALVR | `visionos-app/ALVR/` | See `visionos-app/ALVR/LICENSE` |
| Vivecraft (fork) | `minecraft/VivecraftMod/` | See upstream Vivecraft / GPL terms in that tree |
| ALVR visionOS client | `visionos-app/ALVRClient/` | Project source; ALVR client_core linkage per `visionos-app/VENDORED.md` |

## Your responsibilities

- Apple platform binaries require your own Apple Developer signing and provisioning.
- Minecraft Java Edition and a valid license are required to run the game path.
- Distribution of combined binaries may impose obligations from GPL/LGPL/MIT terms in the vendored trees; see [docs/distribution.md](docs/distribution.md).
